Package: gwasplot
Title: Publication-Ready and Interactive Plots for GWAS Results
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("loukesio", email = "loukesio@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A ggplot2-based toolkit for visualising genome-wide association
    study (GWAS) results. Provides linear Manhattan plots, per-chromosome
    plots and circular (CMplot-style) plots with support for multiple
    concentric trait rings, easy highlighting and labelling of top markers,
    interactive versions via 'ggiraph', and companion tables of top hits
    via 'gt'.
